# retros/v58x_agent_perspective.cyml — Agent's view from the v5.8.x slices true-completion sub-arc
# retros/v58x_back_half.cyml  — v5.8.x back half (slots .49–.65) — Unicode 17 fold, heap two-step bootstraps, foldin closeout
# retros/foldin_arc_v57_v59.cyml — Cross-cycle pattern: sandhi (v5.7.0) / vani (v5.8.0) / niyama (v5.9.0) — receipts + framework, marked for language-agent extension on niyama-direct experience
